  year:  yea, men shall be at fault, and not recognize them <hi type="super">6</hi>
  accurately.  For they belong to
  the reckoning of the year and are truly recorded (thereon) for ever, one in the first portal
  and one in the third, and one in the fourth and one in the sixth, and the year is completed
