  powers of the heaven which revolve in their circular chariots.  And these are the orders of
  the stars, which set in their places, and in their seasons and festivals and months.
  <hi type="super">10</hi> And
  these are the names of those who lead them, who watch that they enter at their times, in
  their orders, in their seasons, in their months, in their periods of dominion, and in their
